Sourcecode::Spellchecker version 0.03
================================

This module can be used to identify common misspellings in source code for a variety of languages (C, C++, Java, Perl, etc.)

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

Test::More

